
To make the LSSTSRD.ps file:

latex LSSTSRD.tex
latex LSSTSRD.tex
makeglos.pl LSSTSRD.glo
latex LSSTSRD.tex
dvips -t letter -o LSSTSRD.ps LSSTSRD.dvi


Note:
Text is in files:   
introduction.tex  
scidrivers.tex  
tables.tex
membership.tex  
appendices.tex  

which are included in the main file LSSTSRD.tex

Two support files are required: pdfrhl.tex and glossary.sty,
and the rest is standard latex. 

